<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2 class="text-decoration-underline">About Our Company</h2>
            <p>Appointify is a leading provider of appointment management solutions, dedicated to simplifying the scheduling process for businesses and individuals alike. Our mission is to streamline appointment booking, reduce scheduling conflicts, and improve overall efficiency.</p>
            <p>With a team of dedicated professionals and cutting-edge technology, we strive to provide intuitive, secure, and reliable software solutions to meet the diverse needs of our clients.</p>
            <p>Founded in 2024, Appointify has rapidly grown to become a trusted partner for businesses seeking efficient appointment management solutions.</p>
        </div>
